data.description: Discover this immaculately maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, nestled on a charming corner lot.  This single-story floor plan provides a practical layout, with the kitchen overlooking the dining and great room areas. As you enter, you'll notice a generously sized flex space, perfect for use as an office or playroom. The owner's suite boasts a walk-in closet and a double vanity in the bathroom. The home has been tastefully updated with wood-look tile throughout the main living areas, and the main bathroom, laundry, and entry have received stylish tile upgrades. Located conveniently close to Austin, San Antonio, Seguin, and San Marcos, this property offers an ideal location for various lifestyles. Don't miss out on the opportunity to schedule a showing today!
